{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "45cec9c3-16da-425f-9543-c2f3f9a649e2", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/45cec9c3-16da-425f-9543-c2f3f9a649e2@1.pkg/1772597668182/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597668910", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/45cec9c3-16da-425f-9543-c2f3f9a649e2@1.pkg/1772597668182/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597668910"}, "identifier": "45cec9c3-16da-425f-9543-c2f3f9a649e2", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>一审题干；二审设问；三审题肢。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>“考试发挥得不错”，对应的因是生活事件；“校园里处处鸟语花香”对应的因素是外部环境，故①②不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>“火冒三丈”表明小勇性格比较刚烈，“外貌有小瑕疵”而自卑是对外貌的执念，故③④；</p>\n\n<p>故本题选D。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（原创）以下是中学生小勇最近一段时期的经历以及影响其情绪的因素，其中匹配正确的是（&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:593px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:49px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">选项</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:369px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">日记节选</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:176px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">影响情绪的因素</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:49px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">①</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:369px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">这次考试发挥得不错，我整天都沉浸在快乐之中</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:176px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">外部环境</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:49px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">②</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:369px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">校园里处处鸟语花香，我的心情变得温暖而愉悦</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:176px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">生活事件</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:49px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">③</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:369px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">同桌不小心踩了我一脚，我火冒三丈，大声吼叫</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:176px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">个人性格特点</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:49px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">④</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:369px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">我的外貌有小瑕疵，我产生了自卑、焦虑的情绪</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:176px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">对事物的观念和看法</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n", "title": "（原创）以下是中学生小勇最近一段时期的经历以及影响其情绪的因素，其中匹配正确的是（  ）选项日记节选影响情绪的因素①这次考试发挥得不错，我整天都沉浸在快乐之中外部环境②校园里处处鸟语花香，我的心情变得温暖而愉悦生活事件③同桌不小心踩了我一脚，我火冒三丈，大声吼叫个人性格特点④我的外貌有小瑕疵，我产生了自卑、焦虑的情绪对事物的观念和看法", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/45cec9c3-16da-425f-9543-c2f3f9a649e2@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754826426324", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①②</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①③&nbsp;</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>②④</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>③④</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>（原创）以下是中学生小勇最近一段时期的经历以及影响其情绪的因素，其中匹配正确的是（&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:593px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:49px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">选项</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:369px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">日记节选</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:176px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">影响情绪的因素</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:49px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">①</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:369px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">这次考试发挥得不错，我整天都沉浸在快乐之中</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:176px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">外部环境</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:49px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">②</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:369px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">校园里处处鸟语花香，我的心情变得温暖而愉悦</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:176px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">生活事件</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:49px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">③</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:369px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">同桌不小心踩了我一脚，我火冒三丈，大声吼叫</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:176px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">个人性格特点</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:49px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">④</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:369px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">我的外貌有小瑕疵，我产生了自卑、焦虑的情绪</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width:176px\">\n\t\t\t<p align=\"center\">对事物的观念和看法</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee